        Gifting Property to Family in Queensland: What Owners Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Transferring a home to a child or family member without payment looks simple on paper. The tax and duty consequences are anything but. Here is what really happens when you gift property in Queensland.
      </p>
